Installation
====================

This project provides XML utilities for the visualization of mechanical systems. It needs fmatvec, Xerces, Xalan, octave. After the installation proceed with the following steps.


1. Checkout from git
--------------------

If not already done, checkout the git tree
# git clone https://github.com/mbsim-env/openmbv.git


2. Run AutoTools
----------------

# aclocal
# autoheader
# libtoolize -c --force
# autoconf
# automake -a -c --force


3. Proceed with configure
-------------------------

See file INSTALL.
